checkers.regex.quals

Annotation Type RegexBottom


  • @TypeQualifier
 @InvisibleQualifier
 @SubtypeOf(value={Regex.class,PartialRegex.class})
 @Target(value={})
public @interface RegexBottom
    Represents the bottom of the Regex qualifier hierarchy. This is used to make the null literal a subtype of all Regex annotations.

    This annotation may not be written in source code; it is an implementation detail of the checker.
